About Me

Hi, my name is Ashley Saleem-West. I'm a web developer based St Albans, a town close. I describe myself as a passionate developer who loves coding, open source, and the web platform ❤️.

Starting as a designer and become aquanted with web development through my personal E-Commerce projects before moving onto E-Service Europe Ltd, to redesign and develop their E-Commerce website.

I like to think of performance and design as two sides of the same coin, which is why I push for great user experiece without a heavy overhead.
